From b033f2a70be78b79bd674bd21fa42fdc1f68fdd9 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Galih Tama <galpt@v.recipes>
Date: Thu, 9 Jul 2026 02:13:30 +0700
Subject: [PATCH 1/6] v4.5: core Infinity scheduler infrastructure

Add struct infinity_ctx to task_struct, futex_waiting flag for IPC
wakeup boost, infinity_sched.c/h algorithm implementation, fork init
in sched_fork(), cfs_rq group_ema/cgroup fields, infinity_version
sysctl, and scheduler Makefile entry.

